2876ea65-7ac0-48a9-9151-2847a267e229.title: Father Lawrence
2876ea65-7ac0-48a9-9151-2847a267e229.text: Hello adventurer, do you seek a quest?

options.text: I am always looking for a quest.
No, I prefer just to kill things.
Can you recommend a good bar?

36eb4f7f-0b5f-418e-9df1-e5d84a1abe69.title: <player>
36eb4f7f-0b5f-418e-9df1-e5d84a1abe69.text: I am always looking for a quest.

640bb7b3-3906-462a-bb34-8bf1dc4c27cf.title: Father Lawrence
640bb7b3-3906-462a-bb34-8bf1dc4c27cf.text:
Well, I see poor Romeo wandering around the square.
I think he may need help.

c26d198a-1dce-4302-8afb-8311a276fc41.title: Father Lawrence
c26d198a-1dce-4302-8afb-8311a276fc41.text:
I was helping him and Juliet to meet, but it became
impossible.

5265aa9f-6b7c-4c8a-a510-f87784fc348b.title: Father Lawrence
5265aa9f-6b7c-4c8a-a510-f87784fc348b.text: I am sure he can use some help.

32cad1c2-df7d-434c-945b-e01060a9fcfd.title: <player>
32cad1c2-df7d-434c-945b-e01060a9fcfd.text: No, I prefer just to kill things.

e28d2d0a-ddbc-410f-8187-4d8e84c4e34c.title: Father Lawrence
e28d2d0a-ddbc-410f-8187-4d8e84c4e34c.text:
That's a fine career in these lands.
There is more that needs killing every day.

2318c17a-e106-419f-9f23-aacfeaad151b.title: <player>
2318c17a-e106-419f-9f23-aacfeaad151b.text: Can you recommend a good bar?

ab4eb466-d915-46b9-94aa-137b957044f8.title: Father Lawrence
ab4eb466-d915-46b9-94aa-137b957044f8.text: Drinking will be the death of you.

aeec4d53-59a2-42fb-afd1-1806d3c8451d.title: Father Lawrence
aeec4d53-59a2-42fb-afd1-1806d3c8451d.text: But the Blue Moon in the city is cheap enough.

33ddef16-bce3-492d-9070-a8605779c050.title: Father Lawrence
33ddef16-bce3-492d-9070-a8605779c050.text:
And providing you buy one drink an hour they let you
stay all night.

c9c96107-8f5b-4e01-af03-c0e4be5d3340.title: Father Lawrence
c9c96107-8f5b-4e01-af03-c0e4be5d3340.text:
''...and let Saradomin light the way for you... ''
Urgh!

910a0b74-91e3-4f90-93bf-bffae08793d1.title: Father Lawrence
910a0b74-91e3-4f90-93bf-bffae08793d1.text: Can't you see that I'm in the middle of a Sermon?!

e5025511-c43e-4416-a760-79d53cc84355.title: Father Lawrence
e5025511-c43e-4416-a760-79d53cc84355.text: But I'm busy delivering a sermon to my congregation!

5d7ef670-f171-48fe-a93a-17a0b92bb6ab.title: <player>
5d7ef670-f171-48fe-a93a-17a0b92bb6ab.text:
Yes, well, it certainly seems like you have a captive
audience!

ce6625cc-80fc-4f6d-a347-f4dd44d5b9e0.title: Father Lawrence
ce6625cc-80fc-4f6d-a347-f4dd44d5b9e0.text:
Ok, ok...what do you want so I can get rid of you and
continue with my sermon?

70ae4c86-9dc0-4e38-a8cb-cff9a3855e38.title: <player>
70ae4c86-9dc0-4e38-a8cb-cff9a3855e38.text: Romeo sent me. He says you may be able to help.

19bfc8ba-34ef-402f-8920-c4b0f334a2d3.title: Father Lawrence
19bfc8ba-34ef-402f-8920-c4b0f334a2d3.text: Ah Romeo, yes. A fine lad, but a little bit confused.

a47c6ec0-e606-48c3-844e-14c25d9b45a4.title: <player>
a47c6ec0-e606-48c3-844e-14c25d9b45a4.text:
Yes, very confused....Anyway, Romeo wishes to be
married to Juliet! She must be rescued from her
father's control!

85c2bfc0-ac6a-4462-9964-787b42fcbdc5.title: Father Lawrence
85c2bfc0-ac6a-4462-9964-787b42fcbdc5.text:
I agree, and I think I have an idea! A potion to make
her appear dead...

ea2bc432-c8c0-4cbc-aa76-1c7ac0fa6526.title: <player>
ea2bc432-c8c0-4cbc-aa76-1c7ac0fa6526.text: Dead! Sounds a bit creepy to me...but please, continue.

1661c2b3-a940-4ba6-94ea-2574135d70b7.title: Father Lawrence
1661c2b3-a940-4ba6-94ea-2574135d70b7.text:
The potion will only make Juliet 'appear' dead...then
she'll be taken to the crypt...

64152883-1cd5-44b6-8259-cad5cb02799e.title: <player>
64152883-1cd5-44b6-8259-cad5cb02799e.text:
Crypt! Again...very creepy! You must have some
strange hobbies.

e8d96afb-ef3d-4cce-a528-d5c7a0941140.title: Father Lawrence
e8d96afb-ef3d-4cce-a528-d5c7a0941140.text:
hen Romeo can collect her from the crypt! Go to the
Apothecary, tell him I sent you and that you'll need a
'Cadava' potion.

c06f761e-61fb-4611-aecd-f2d484533bdb.title: <player>
c06f761e-61fb-4611-aecd-f2d484533bdb.text:
Apart from the strong overtones of death, this is
turning out to be a real love story.

d7c43e05-0ee7-48cd-b173-dce033845f46.title: Father Lawrence
d7c43e05-0ee7-48cd-b173-dce033845f46.text:
Ah, have you found the Apothecary yet? Remember,
Cadava potion, for Juliet.

9ba58b85-5ddc-411e-8331-a55d11917535.title: Father Lawrence
9ba58b85-5ddc-411e-8331-a55d11917535.text:
Good! Good work! Ok, take it to Juliet, she's expecting
you. I'll talk to Romeo and make sure he knows what
to do.

8fe01550-b135-406d-a1cd-d29a39ebc1da.title: Father Lawrence
8fe01550-b135-406d-a1cd-d29a39ebc1da.text: Oh to be a father in the times of whiskey.

bd75f9df-c866-44cf-aae1-f19035bea982.title: Father Lawrence
bd75f9df-c866-44cf-aae1-f19035bea982.text: I sing and I drink and I wake up in gutters.

b0cd813f-5384-41a5-a509-9695dca6744e.title: Father Lawrence
b0cd813f-5384-41a5-a509-9695dca6744e.text: Top of the morning to you.
